divs: Sighting DetailsPictures of crafts over St. Mary's River. I did not know they were there until I look at them later. There are two different kinds of crafts and I have no idea what they are. One od they is like a tri-circular and glow and the other is a boomarang shape.
Summary: Picture taken of a rainbow over St. Mary's River. When I looked at the pictures I noticed the crafts.
